'''navbox''' - Template for game page navigation on games.darkrepos.com

==Description==

Creates a navigation box with links to standard sub-pages for a game. Automatically generates links to ROM Map, RAM Map, SRAM Map, TBL, and Values pages.

==Usage==

===Basic Usage===
<pre>
{{navbox|Dragon_Quest_III_(SNES)}}
</pre>

===With Custom Pages===
<pre>
{{navbox
| game = Dragon_Quest_III_(SNES)
| rom_map = yes
| ram_map = yes
| sram_map = yes
| tbl = yes
| values = yes
| extra1 = Monsters
| extra2 = Items
| extra3 = Maps
}}
</pre>

==Parameters==

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Required !! Default !! Description
|-
| game (or 1) || Yes || — || Game folder name
|-
| rom_map || No || yes || Include ROM Map link
|-
| ram_map || No || yes || Include RAM Map link
|-
| sram_map || No || no || Include SRAM Map link
|-
| tbl || No || yes || Include TBL link
|-
| values || No || yes || Include Values link
|-
| extra1-5 || No || — || Additional custom page links
|}

==Example Output==

{{navbox|Dragon_Warrior_IV_(NES)|sram_map=yes|extra1=Map_List|extra2=Known_Dumps}}

==Styling==

The navigation box uses a consistent style:
* Blue header bar
* Light gray background
* Horizontal layout for standard pages
* Automatic link generation to sub-pages

